'''第81届奥斯卡颁奖典礼'''是[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]旨在奖励[[2008年电影|2008年最优秀电影]]的一场晚会，于2009年2月22日[[太平洋时区|PST]]下午17点30分（[[北美东部时区|EST]]晚上20点30分）开始在[[美国|美国]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]][[好莱坞|好莱坞]]的[[杜比剧院|杜比剧院]]举行，共计颁发了24座[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]（又称[[学院奖|学院奖]]）。男演员[[休·杰克曼|休·杰克曼]]首次担任[[主持人|主持人]]，颁奖典礼通过[[美国广播公司|ABC]]在美国直播<ref>{{cite news | last=Vena |first=Joyce | title=Hugh Jackman Will Host The 2009 Oscars, Academy Confirms |archivedate=2013-10-20 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1601239/hugh-jackman-will-host-2009-oscars-academy-confirms.jhtml | work=''MTV'' | publisher=Viacom Media Networks | date=2008-12-12 | accessdate=2013-10-30 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131020094212/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1601239/hugh-jackman-will-host-2009-oscars-academy-confirms.jhtml}}</ref>，吸引了[[北美|北美]]地区近3700万观众收看。两个[[星期|星期]]前的2月7日，[[謝茜嘉·比爾|謝茜嘉·比爾]]在[[比佛利山_(加利福尼亞州)|比佛利山]]的[[比佛利山威尔希尔酒店|威尔希尔丽晶酒店]]主持颁发了[[奥斯卡科技成果奖|奥斯卡科技成果奖]]<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2013-10-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131022205820/http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2009/02/jessica-biel-em.html |url=http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2009/02/jessica-biel-em.html | last=O'Neil | first=Tom | title=Jessica Biel emcees sci-tech Oscars | date= 2009-02-03 |work= Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |accessdate=2013-10-30}}</ref>。

《[[贫民窟的百万富翁|贫民窟的百万富翁]]》赢得了包括[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片]]和[[奥斯卡最佳导演奖|导演]]在内的八项大奖，成为这个夜晚的最大赢家<ref>{{cite news |title='Slumdog' makes history, sweeps Oscars |work=CNN |publisher=Time Warner |date=2009-02-22 |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/Movies/02/23/oscar.night/ |accessdate=2013-10-30 | last=Leopold |first=Todd |archivedate=2009-04-29 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20090429210414/http://edition.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/Movies/02/23/oscar.night/}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2009/feb/23/entertainment/et-oscar23 | last=Horn | first=John | title='Slumdog' strikes it rich with 8 Oscar wins | date= 2009-02-23 |work= Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |accessdate=2013-10-30 |archivedate=2013-10-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131022133308/http://articles.latimes.com/2009/feb/23/entertainment/et-oscar23}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Vancheri |first=Barbara |title=Top Dog: Passage to India proves golden for Mumbai fairy tale |url=http://www.post-gazette.com/ae/2009/02/23/Top-Dog-Passage-to-India-proves-golden-for-Mumbai-fairy-tale/stories/200902230181 |work=Pittsburgh Post-Gazette |publisher=Block Communications |accessdate=2013-10-30 |date=2009-02-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014163048/http://www.post-gazette.com/stories/life/seen/top-dog-passage-to-india-proves-golden-for-mumbai-fairy-tale-331143/ |archivedate=2013-10-14 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。其它获奖电影包括获奖三项的《[[本杰明·巴顿奇事|本杰明·巴顿奇事]]》，获奖两项的《[[黑暗骑士|黑暗骑士]]》和《[[米尔克_(电影)|米尔克]]》，以及获奖一项的《[[送行者：禮儀師的樂章|入殓师]]》、《[[公爵夫人_(电影)|浮華一世情]]》、《[[回憶積木屋|回憶積木屋]]》、《[[走钢丝的人|走钢丝的人]]》、《[[朗读者_(电影)|朗读者]]》、《{{link-en|微笑的苹吉|Smile Pinki}}》、《{{link-en|玩具岛|Toyland (2007 film)}}》、《[[午夜巴塞罗那|午夜巴塞罗那]]》和《[[瓦力_(電影)|瓦力]]》。

==获奖和提名==
第81届奥斯卡金像奖提名名单於[[太平洋时区|PST]]2009年1月22日早上5点38分（[[协调世界时|UTC]]下午13点38分）由学院主席西德尼·甘尼斯（{{lang|en|Sidney Ganis}}）和男演员[[科力士·韋德加|科力士·韋德加]]一起在[[比佛利山_(加利福尼亞州)|比佛利山]]的[[塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院|塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院]]公布<ref name="ForestWhitaker2009">{{cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2009/20090120.html |title=Forest Whitaker to Join Academy President Sid Ganis for Oscar Nominations |date=2009-01-20 |work=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences |accessdate=2013-10-31 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131022202218/http://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2009/20090120.html | archivedate= 2013-10-22 | deadurl= no}}</ref>。《本杰明·巴顿奇事》以多达13项提名领跑，是历史上第9部获得这么多项提名的电影<ref name="Oscar facts and figures">{{cite news |archivedate=2013-10-04 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131004233055/http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2009/01/oscar-nominat-1.html |url=http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2009/01/oscar-nominat-1.html |title=Oscar nominations: Fascinating facts, figures and milestones | last = O'Neil | first=Tom | date=2009-01-22 |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |accessdate=2013-10-31}}</ref>，《贫民窟的百万富翁》则以10项提名紧随其后<ref name="ForestWhitaker2009" />。

获奖名单在2009年2月22日举行的颁奖典礼上公布<ref>{{cite news |title=Academy Award winners and nominees |publisher=Time Warner |work=CNN |date=2009-02-22 |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/Movies/02/22/oscar.nominees.full.list/index.html |accessdate=2013-10-31 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120721141150/http://edition.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/Movies/02/22/oscar.nominees.full.list/index.html | archivedate= 2012-07-21 | deadurl= no}}</ref>，《贫民窟的百万富翁》成为历史上第11部没有获得任何一项演员表演类奖项提名但却最终夺得最佳影片奖的电影<ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2012-10-21 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.tvguide.com/news/2009-oscar-predictions-1003134.aspx |title=Oscars: Who Will Win and Who Will Surprise? |first=Joyce |last=Eng |date=2009-02-20 |work=TV Guide |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20121021031910/http://www.tvguide.com/news/2009-oscar-predictions-1003134.aspx}}</ref>。[[西恩·潘|西恩·潘]]则成为了第9位获得第二座[[奥斯卡最佳男主角奖|男主角奖]]的演员<ref>{{cite news |deadurl=no |url=http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2009/02/oscar-news-411.html |title=Sean Penn is the ninth actor to win two lead Oscars | last = O'Neil | first=Tom | date=2009-02-23 |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archivedate=2013-03-08 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130308055511/http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2009/02/oscar-news-411.html}}</ref>。获男配角奖的[[希斯·莱杰|希斯·莱杰]]成为历史上第二位过世后获表演奖的演员，第一位是[[彼得·芬奇|彼得·芬奇]]，他曾因《[[广播电视网|广播电视网]]》获[[第50届奥斯卡金像奖|第50届奥斯卡金像奖]]男主角奖，但他已于颁奖典礼举办前两个月（1977年1月）去世<ref name="Heath Ledger Oscar">{{cite news|url=http://theenvelope.latimes.com/awards/oscars/la-et-oscarledger23-2009feb23,0,5458027.story |title=For Heath Ledger, a bittersweet salute |last=Johnson |first=Reed |date=2009-02-23 |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archivedate=2013-06-26 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130626094056/http://theenvelope.latimes.com/awards/oscars/la-et-oscarledger23-2009feb23%2C0%2C5458027.story }}</ref>。学院在与莱杰远在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]的家人交流过后，决定由莱杰的女儿玛蒂尔达·罗斯·莱杰（{{lang|en|Matilda Rose Ledger}}）保有这座小金人。但由于她尚年幼，所以必须要到2023年满18岁生日后才能获得其全部所有权<ref>{{cite web |last=Pond |first=Steve |title=Matilda Ledger Designated The Owner Of Heath's Potential Oscar |archivedate=2013-06-03 |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2009/02/18/matilda-ledger-designated_n_167843.html |work=The Huffington Post |deadurl=no |publisher=AOL |accessdate=2013-11-01 |date=2009-02-18 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130603070601/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2009/02/18/matilda-ledger-designated_n_167843.html}}</ref>。而在这以前，她的母亲，女演员[[蜜雪兒·威廉絲|蜜雪兒·威廉絲]]将负责保管奖座<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.eonline.com/news/100747/why-can-t-li-l-matilda-have-heath-s-potential-oscar |title=Why Can't Li'l Matilda Have Heath's (Potential) Oscar? |date=2009-02-19 |first=Leslie |last=Gornstein |work=''E!'' |publisher=NBCUniversal |accessdate=2013-11-01 |archive-date=2013-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103124010/http://www.eonline.com/news/100747/why-can-t-li-l-matilda-have-heath-s-potential-oscar |dead-url=no }}</ref>。莱杰的家人出席了颁奖典礼，他的双亲代替他上台领了奖<ref name="Heath Ledger Oscar" />。另外，动画长片《瓦力》获得了6项提名，追平了1991年的《[[美女与野兽_(1991年电影)|美女与野兽]]》在[[第64届奥斯卡金像奖|第64届奥斯卡金像奖]]中创下的获提名最多的动画片纪录<ref name="Oscar facts and figures" />。

