==典礼资讯==
[[File:HughJackmanHWOFDec2012.jpg|thumb]]担任第81届奥斯卡颁奖典礼的主持人]]
由于过去几届奥斯卡颁奖典礼的收视观众人数有所下降，美国电影艺术与科学学院于是与全新的制作团队签约，希望重振奖项和晚会的声威。2008年9月，学院选择了[[制片人|制片人]]比尔·康顿和劳伦斯·马克共同负责本期典礼的电视转播<ref>{{cite news|url=http://theenvelope.latimes.com/awards/oscars/env-et-oscarproducer25-2008sep25,0,6564123.story |title=Laurence Mark, Bill Condon to produce Oscars |date=2008-09-24 |first=Susan |last=King |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archivedate=2008-10-16 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081016090544/http://theenvelope.latimes.com/awards/oscars/env-et-oscarproducer25-2008sep25%2C0%2C6564123.story }}</ref>。近三个月后，[[男演员|男演员]]休·杰克曼获选成为本届盛会的主持人，他之前曾从2003年至2005年连续主持了三届[[托尼奖|托尼奖颁奖典礼]]<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2009-05-01 |deadurl=no |url=http://movies.tvguide.com/Movie-News/Oscar-Awards-Hugh-1000798.aspx | title=Hugh Jackman to Host 2009 Oscars | date= 2008-12-12 |first=Joyce |last=Eng |work=TV Guide |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20090501064736/http://movies.tvguide.com/Movie-News/Oscar-Awards-Hugh-1000798.aspx}}</ref>。颁奖典礼开始前几天，杰克曼表示自己对其充满期待，很高兴可以参加晚会的筹备工作<ref>{{cite news |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/Oscars/hugh-jackman-hosting-oscars-night-celebration/story?id=6895832#.UbAQLdgzRA0 |title=Hugh Jackman on Hosting Oscars: 'A Night of Celebration' |last=Escherich |first=Katie |work=''ABC News'' |publisher=The Walt Disney Company |date=2009-02-20 |accessdate=2013-10-31 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-10-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031141311/http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/Oscars/hugh-jackman-hosting-oscars-night-celebration/story?id=6895832}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20254914,00.html |title=Hugh Jackman: Oscars' Sexiest Host? |date=2009-01-28 |first=Miisy |last=Schwartz |work=Entertainment Weekly |publisher=Time Warner |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archivedate=2009-04-27 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090427082821/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20254914%2C00.html }}</ref>。

典礼一个显著的变化是将电视转播引入到制作中。为了给奖项增加悬念，引起观众的好奇心，康顿和马克宣布所有颁奖和表演嘉宾的身份都将予以保密<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2012-11-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20121103185807/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2009-02-19-the-oscar-11_N.htm |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2009-02-19-the-oscar-11_N.htm |title=The Oscar 11: Team aims to revive awards' telecast |first=Anthony |last=Breznican |work=USA Today |publisher=Gannett Company |date=2009-02-19 |accessdate=2013-10-31}}</ref>。本届颁奖典礼的另一个特色就是管弦乐团将直接在舞台上演奏曲目，而不是像以往那样处在舞台下的一个地下室中<ref>{{cite web |title=I’m with the band! Oscars stage design revealed |url=http://www.today.com/id/29299773/ns/today-today_entertainment/t/im-band-oscars-stage-design-revealed/ |work=NBC News |publisher=NBCUniversal |accessdate=2013-10-31 |date=2009-02-20 |archivedate=2013-10-31 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031142219/http://www.today.com/id/29299773/ns/today-today_entertainment/t/im-band-oscars-stage-design-revealed/}}</ref>。另一个与往届不同的是，演员表演类奖项将请来该奖项的以往五位获奖者颁奖，而不再是只有一或两位<ref>{{cite news | archivedate=2013-10-31 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131031142501/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2009-02-23-oscar-telecast-comparison_N.htm?hiddenMacValue=0&hiddenMacPrintValue=0 |url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2009-02-23-oscar-telecast-comparison_N.htm?hiddenMacValue=0&hiddenMacPrintValue=0#2003 |title=Oscar showtime: This year vs. Others |work=USA Today |publisher=Gannett Company |date=2009-02-23 |last=Clark |first=Mike |accessdate=2013-10-31}}</ref>。学院还宣布自奥斯卡颁奖典礼开始通过电视转播以来，电影公司将首次获准在节目中插播广告来宣布即将上映的电影<ref>{{cite news |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-10-31 |url=http://variety.com/2008/film/news/film-ads-to-run-during-oscar-telecast-1117993650/ |title=Film ads to run during Oscar telecast |first=Timothy M. |last= Gray |coauthor=Cynthia Littleton |date=2008-10-08 |work=Variety |publisher=PMC |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131031142824/http://variety.com/2008/film/news/film-ads-to-run-during-oscar-telecast-1117993650/}}</ref>，此外，晚会的电视转播结束并播出字幕时，将会播出一个2009年即将上映新片的蒙太奇<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.moviefone.com/2009/02/23/2009-academy-awards-best-and-worst-recap/ |title=2009 Academy Awards Best and Worst Recap |date=2009-02-23 |first=Erik |last=Davis |work=''Moviefone'' |publisher=AOL |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031143132/http://news.moviefone.com/2009/02/23/2009-academy-awards-best-and-worst-recap/ |archivedate=2013-10-31 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

另外还有多人参与了颁奖典礼的制作。[[克里斯·哈里森|克里斯·哈里森]]主持了“通向奥斯卡之路”（{{lang|en|Road to the Oscars}}），这是个奥斯卡颁奖典礼网站上的幕后视频[[博客|博客]]，每周都会更新<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.tvweek.com/news/2009/02/oscarcom_announces_web_shows.php |title=Oscar.com Announces Web Shows |first=Vlada |last=Gelman |work=TelevisionWeek |publisher=Crain Communications |date=2009-02-18 |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archive-date=2013-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102213422/http://www.tvweek.com/news/2009/02/oscarcom_announces_web_shows.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{link-en|大卫·罗克韦尔|David Rockwell}}为晚会设计了新的装饰和舞台<ref>{{cite web |last=Brown |first=Patricia Leigh |title=The Little Gold Man in a New Blue World |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/02/15/movies/awardsseason/15brow.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 |work=The New York Times |publisher=The New York Times Company |accessdate=2013-10-31 |date=2009-02-12 |archive-date=2016-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160717122826/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/02/15/movies/awardsseason/15brow.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。电影[[历史学家|历史学家]]兼作家{{link-en|罗伯特·奥斯本|Robert Osborne}}在[[好莱坞和高地中心|好莱坞和高地中心]]迎接来宾进入会场<ref>{{cite news |title=Robert Osborne to Greet Celebrities on Oscar’s Red Carpet |url=http://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2009/20090217.html |work=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences |publisher=AMPAS |accessdate=2013-10-31 |date=2009-02-17 |archivedate=2013-10-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131022202438/http://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2009/20090217.html}}</ref>。电影[[导演|导演]][[贾德·阿帕图|贾德·阿帕图]]拍摄了一个喜剧片断，其中有[[塞斯·羅根|塞斯·羅根]]和[[詹姆斯·弗朗科|詹姆斯·弗朗科]]回归表演他们在《[[菠萝快车|菠萝快车]]》中的片断<ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2012-10-09 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.tvguide.com/News/2009-Oscar-Moments-1003234.aspx |title=Top Oscar Moments: Tears for a Joker, Million-Dollar Babies and More |first=Joyce |last=Eng |date=2009-02-23 |work=TV Guide |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20121009051817/http://www.tvguide.com/News/2009-Oscar-Moments-1003234.aspx}}</ref>。导演[[巴茲·雷曼|巴茲·雷曼]]制作了一个歌舞表演曲目，向历史上的[[歌舞片|歌舞片]]致敬<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2013-09-30 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7905056.stm |last=Sutherland |first=Ben|title=Jackman on song at his first Oscars  |accessdate=2013-10-31 |work=BBC News |date=2009-02-23 |publisher=BBC |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130930232650/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7905056.stm}}</ref>。

[[彼得·蓋布瑞爾|彼得·蓋布瑞爾]]原定将在颁奖典礼时上台演唱《瓦力》中获原创歌曲奖提名的片尾曲“{{lang|en|Down to Earth}}”，但他在得知自己只能唱65秒钟后回绝了这次表演的机会<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2013-10-31 |deadurl=no |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2009-02-12-gabriel-oscars_N.htm?csp=34 |title=Peter Gabriel won't perform at Oscars |work=USA Today |publisher=Gannett Company |date=2009-02-13 |last=Breznican |first=Anthony |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031145445/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2009-02-12-gabriel-oscars_N.htm?csp=34 }}</ref>。蓋布瑞爾仍然出席了典礼，但这首歌曲则改由歌手[[約翰傳奇|約翰傳奇]]和索韦托福音合唱团共同演唱<ref>{{cite web |last=Donahue |first=Ann |title='Slumdog Millionaire' Sweeps Music Oscars |archivedate=2013-06-30 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130630040500/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/269365/slumdog-millionaire-sweeps-music-oscars |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/269365/slumdog-millionaire-sweeps-music-oscars |work=Billboard |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |accessdate=2013-10-31 |date=2009-02-23}}</ref>。

===提名电影票房表现===
与之前几年的情况一样，本届奥斯卡金像奖提名作品也以低成本独立制片作品为主<ref>{{cite news |url=http://variety.com/2009/tv/reviews/the-81st-annual-academy-awards-from-the-couch-1200473511/ |title=How the Oscars Became the Emmys | last = Corliss | first=Richard | date=2009-02-12 |work=Time |publisher=Time Warner |deadurl=no |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archivedate=2013-10-23 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131023213153/http://variety.com/2009/tv/reviews/the-81st-annual-academy-awards-from-the-couch-1200473511/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Cieply |first=Michael |title=Academy Expands Best-Picture Pool to 10 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/25/movies/25oscars.html |work=The New York Times|publisher=The New York Times Company |accessdate=2013-10-31 |date=2009-06-24 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130722095539/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/25/movies/25oscars.html |archivedate=2013-07-22}}</ref>。不过还是有一部获最佳影片提名的电影在提名公布前就收获了超过1亿[[美元|美元]]的[[票房|票房]]，之前的一年则一部都没有<ref name="Benjamin Button Oscar">{{cite web |last=Eller |first=Claudia |title='Benjamin Button's' Oscar nominations may not pay off for Paramount |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2009/jan/23/business/fi-button23 |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |accessdate=2013-10-31 |date=2009-02-23 |archivedate=2013-10-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022225726/http://articles.latimes.com/2009/jan/23/business/fi-button23 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。5部获最佳影片提名的电影在提名人布时的总票房成绩为1亿8670万6631美元，平均每部3734万1326美元<ref name="boxofficeoscars81">{{cite web |archivedate=2013-10-05 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131005123504/http://boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=2008&view=fulldetail&p=.htm |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=2008&view=fulldetail&p=.htm |title=2008 Academy Award Nominations and Winner for Best Picture|work=''Box Office Mojo'' |publisher=Amazon.com |accessdate=2013-10-31}}</ref>。

截止提名公布时，《本杰明·巴顿奇事》是获最佳影片提名的五部电影中票房成绩最好的一部，其在美国的收入为1亿零438万8850美元<ref name="Benjamin Button Oscar" />，排在第二位的是收入4471万1799美元的《贫民窟的百万富翁》，其后分别是收入2065万5400美元的《米尔克》，收入888万8701美元的《福斯特对话尼克松》和收入806万1881美元的《朗读者》<ref name="boxofficeoscars81" />。在2008年美国电影票房前50强的电影中，有9部电影获得了一共33项提名，其中《黑暗骑士》（[[冠军|冠军]]）、《瓦力》（第五名）、《功夫熊猫》（第六名）、《闪电狗》（第19位）、《热带惊雷》（第20位）和《本杰明·巴顿奇事》获得了最佳影片、导演、动画长片或编剧和表演类奖项提名<ref name="boxofficemojooscars">{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?view=allmovies&yr=2008&sort=rank&order=ASC&p=.htm |title=2008 Oscar nominations and wins by movie |publisher=Amazon.com |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-10-31 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131005231750/http://boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=2008&view=allmovies&sort=rank&order=ASC&p=.htm | archivedate= 2013-10-05}}</ref>，另外几位票房50强中获得提名的电影分别是《钢铁侠》（[[亚军|亚军]]）、《刺客联盟》（第16位）和《地狱男爵2：黄金军团》（第41位）<ref name="boxofficemojooscars" />。

===伪造的获奖名单泄露事件===
奖项投票结束后不久，[[互联网|互联网]]上出现了一个名单，声称是本届奥斯卡奖角逐的最终结果。名单声称有学院主席西德尼·甘尼斯的签名，称[[米基·洛克|米基·洛克]]将夺得男主角奖，凯特·温丝莱特获女主角奖，[[艾美·亞當斯|艾美·亞當斯]]会赢得女配角奖，而男配角奖则属于希斯·莱杰，最佳影片奖得主是《贫民窟的百万富翁》<ref>{{cite news |deadurl=no |url=http://www.businessinsider.com/leaked-list-of-oscar-winners-2009-2 |title=Leaked List Of Oscar Winners Is Fake |last=Carlson |first=Nicholas |work=Business Insiser |date=2009-02-21 |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archivedate=2013-10-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131026070054/http://www.businessinsider.com/leaked-list-of-oscar-winners-2009-2}}</ref>。美国电影艺术与科学学院发言人莱斯利·昂格尔（{{lang|en|Leslie Unger}}）之后透露，这份名单“完全是伪造的”，[[普华永道|普华永道]]才刚刚开始点票<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.eonline.com/news/100779/leaked-oscar-winner-list-is-a-complete-fraud |title=Leaked Oscar-Winner List Is a "Complete Fraud" |work=E! |publisher=NBCUniversal |first=Natalie |last=Finn |date=2009-02-19 |accessdate=2013-10-31 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018110027/http://www.eonline.com/news/100779/leaked-oscar-winner-list-is-a-complete-fraud | archivedate= 2012-10-18 | deadurl= no}}</ref>。

===专业评价===
本届颁奖典礼获得的媒体评价褒贬不一，部分媒体给出了较为正面的评价。《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》电视评论员罗伯特·比安科（{{lang|en|Robert Bianco}}）对主持人休·杰克曼的评价一般，但称赞了两位制片人康顿和马克在没有牺牲好莱坞魅力的情况下让晚会有了更快速和亲密的感觉<ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2012-11-05 |deadurl=no |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2009-02-23-oscar-telecast_n.htm |title=For this Oscar show, intimacy, glamour share the stage |work=USA Today |publisher=Gannett Company |last=Bianco |first=Robert |date=2009-02-23 |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20121105224217/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2009-02-23-oscar-telecast_N.htm}}</ref>。《[[名利场_(杂志)|名利场]]》专栏作家朱利安·桑克顿（{{lang|en|Julian Sancton}}）对杰克曼的主持给出高度评价，称奥斯卡颁奖典礼过去几年请的都是像[[喬恩·史都華|喬恩·史都華]]、[[艾倫·狄珍妮|艾倫·狄珍妮]]和[[史提夫·馬丁|史提夫·馬丁]]这样爱说俏皮话，但却会影响节目光彩的主持人，今年终于找来一个愿意出力气流一身大汗的了<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/online/oscars/2009/02/book-hugh-jackman-for-the-next-ten-years-oscars |title=Book Hugh Jackman For the Next Ten Years, Oscars |first=Julian |last=Sancton |work=Vanity Fair |publisher=Condé Nast Publications |date=2009-02-23 |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archivedate=2013-07-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130715072225/http://www.vanityfair.com/online/oscars/2009/02/book-hugh-jackman-for-the-next-ten-years-oscars }}</ref>。影评人[[罗杰·埃伯特|罗杰·埃伯特]]也称赞了杰克曼的表现，称他是个很有魅力的主持人。而对于节目本身，埃伯特表示“这是我所看过最棒的奥斯卡颁奖典礼，而我看的也真是够多的了”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.rogerebert.com/rogers-journal/the-oscars-are-outsourced |title=The Oscars are Outsourced |work=Chicago Sun-Times |publisher=Sun Times Media Group |date=2009-02-23 |first=Roger | last=Ebert |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130507121635/http://www.rogerebert.com/rogers-journal/the-oscars-are-outsourced |archivedate=2013-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

其它部分媒体对节目的看法更为负面。《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》专栏作家玛丽·麦克纳马拉（{{lang|en|Mary McNamara}}）批评主持人杰克曼“抹杀了[[乌玛·瑟曼|乌玛]]和[[奥普拉·温弗瑞|奥普拉]]的所有回忆”，与[[大卫·莱特曼|大卫·莱特曼]]于1995年主持的[[第67屆奧斯卡金像獎|第67届奥斯卡颁奖典礼]]所获负面评价较为类似<ref>{{cite news|archivedate=2013-06-02 |url=http://theenvelope.latimes.com/awards/oscars/la-et-oscarreview23-2009feb23,0,5636262.story |title=The Oscars show itself was puttin' on the fritz |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |date=2009-02-23 |first=Mary |last=McNamara |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130602074838/http://www.theenvelope.latimes.com/awards/oscars/la-et-oscarreview23-2009feb23%2C0%2C5636262.story }}</ref>。《[[时代|时代]]》电视评论员詹姆斯·邦尼沃兹克（{{lang|en|James Poniewozik}}）认为，杰克曼虽然很有魅力，但他并没有作出什么超越，也没有试图做到这一点。他还指出，节目中虽然有不少富娱乐性的瞬间，但总体上还是存在着节奏性的问题<ref>{{cite news |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archivedate=2012-10-20 |deadurl=no |url=http://entertainment.time.com/2009/02/23/the-morning-after-oscars-old-song-and-dance/ |title=The Morning After: Oscar's Old Song and Dance |work=Time |publisher=Time Warner |date=2009-02-23 | first=James | last=Poniewozik |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020201740/http://entertainment.time.com/2009/02/23/the-morning-after-oscars-old-song-and-dance/}}</ref>。《[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]》的莫琳·瑞恩（{{lang|en|Maureen Ryan}}）形容整场节目就像是得了躁郁症，歇力想要带来一些老传统的魅力花招。她还批评表演类奖项多位颁奖嘉宾分别称赞提名人演技的做法减慢了节目的速度<ref>{{cite news |accessdate=2013-11-01 |url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2009-02-23/entertainment/0902220466_1_montage-oscar-producers-oscar-broadcast |title=New format, host are unable to rescue a plodding telecast |work=Chicago Tribune |publisher=Tribune Company |date=2009-02-23 |first=Maureen |last=Ryan |archive-date=2013-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102193652/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2009-02-23/entertainment/0902220466_1_montage-oscar-producers-oscar-broadcast |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===收视率和获奖===
本届颁奖典礼通过美国广播公司在美国直播，其播出时段里平均有3694万观众收看，与[[第80屆奧斯卡金像獎|去年创下历史新低的晚会]]相比提高了13%<ref name="zaprabcatings">{{cite news | first=Robert | last=Seidman | title=Top ABC Primetime Shows week of February 16–22, 2009 | archivedate=2012-10-25 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025100528/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2009/02/24/top-abc-primetime-shows-week-of-february-16-22-2009/13418/ | url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2009/02/24/top-abc-primetime-shows-week-of-february-16-22-2009/13418/ | work=''TVbytheNumbers'' | publisher=Zap2it | date=2009-02-24 | accessdate=2013-10-31 }}</ref><ref name="tvlineoscar">{{cite news | first=Josef | last=Adelian | title=Oscar TV Ratings: Beter, But Not Good |deadurl=no |url=http://www.tvweek.com/news/2009/02/oscar_tv_ratings_better_but_no.php | work = ''TV Line'' | publisher=PMC | date=2009-02-24 | accessdate=2013-10-31 |archivedate=2012-01-12 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120112160740/http://www.tvweek.com/news/2009/02/oscar_tv_ratings_better_but_no.php}}</ref>而所有曾观看部分播出时段节目的观众总数则有约6848万。根据尼尔森收视率调查的数据，本届颁奖典礼的成绩也高于去年，在18至49岁年龄段人群中有12.1%的收视率<ref name="zapratings">{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2009/02/23/81st-academy-awards-averages-363-million-up-42-million-from-last-year/13316/ |title=81st Academy Awards averages 36.3 million up 4.2 million from last year |publisher=Zap2it |date=2009-02-23 |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archive-date=2013-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103131755/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2009/02/23/81st-academy-awards-averages-363-million-up-42-million-from-last-year/13316/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2009年7月，颁奖典礼获得了第61届[[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]的10项提名<ref>{{cite web |title=Primetime Emmy Award Database |url=http://www.emmys.com/awards/nominations/award-search?search_api_views_fulltext=81st+Academy&submit=Search&search_api_views_fulltext_1=&search_api_views_fulltext_3=&search_api_views_fulltext_2=&search_api_views_fulltext_4=&field_nominations_year=All&field_nomination_category=All |work=''Academy of Television Arts and Sciences'' |publisher=ATAS |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102192530/http://www.emmys.com/awards/nominations/award-search?search_api_views_fulltext=81st+Academy&submit=Search&search_api_views_fulltext_1=&search_api_views_fulltext_3=&search_api_views_fulltext_2=&search_api_views_fulltext_4=&field_nominations_year=All&field_nomination_category=All |archive-date=2013-11-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，并在两个月后成功获得了四项大奖，其中包括杰出编舞，杰出原创音乐和歌词，杰出电影剪辑短片和综艺、音乐或特别节目类杰出音效奖<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.eonline.com/news/145090/complete-list-of-winners-from-the-2009-emmy-awards |title=Complete List of Winners From the 2009 Emmy Awards |date=2009-09-13 |work=''E!'' |publisher=NBCUniversal |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archive-date=2013-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103113637/http://www.eonline.com/news/145090/complete-list-of-winners-from-the-2009-emmy-awards |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2012-11-09 |deadurl=no |url=http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2009/09/emmy-awards-tv-news-justin-timberlake-oscars-hugh-jackman-story.html | last=O'Neil | first=Tom | title=Who's really surprised? Oscars upstage Justin Timberlake at the Emmys | date= 2009-09-21 |work= Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |accessdate=2013-10-31 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20121109024226/http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2009/09/emmy-awards-tv-news-justin-timberlake-oscars-hugh-jackman-story.html}}</ref>。

